    "en": {
      "title": "The travel ban against Cabral is extended",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Colombo Additional Magistrate Harshana Kekunawela ordered today (25th) to extend the travel ban imposed against former Central Bank Governor Mr. Ajith Nivard Cabral until the 26th of October.",
        "Ajit Nivard Cabral, former Governor of the Central Bank, for criminal breach of trust, criminal breach of trust by a banker, dishonest and misappropriation of money, Ordinance No. 07 of 1937 (Amendment) No. 56 (a) ( 1) This foreign travel ban was imposed in relation to the complaint filed by the former Mr. Rajith Keerthy Tennakoon that he had committed an offense under (a)."
      ],
